            <title>[SPARK-8099] In yarn-cluster mode, &quot;--executor-cores&quot; can&apos;t be setted into SparkConf</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-8099</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
